## Rebuilding topics (only if needed)

In the notebook (needs `netw` + `isa_precomputed.pkl` loaded):
```python
import pickle
d = pickle.load(open("isa_precomputed.pkl", "rb"))
isa_ancestors, ic = d["isa_ancestors"], d["ic"]
exec(open("build_topics.py").read())
```
Then check quality:
```python
exec(open("diagnose_topics.py").read())
```

